headline: Solar Foods Opens First Commercial Solein Protein Factory
summary: Solar Foods commences commercial production of Solein, a protein made from air and electricity via gas fermentation.

headline: Air Protein Breaks Ground on Commercial Production Facility
summary: Air Protein starts building its first large-scale facility for creating protein from air using gas fermentation.

headline: Bolt Threads Partners with Luxury Brand on Mylo Mushroom Leather Goods
summary: Partnership scales mushroom leather into luxury market, highlighting sustainable material adoption in fashion.

headline: Perfect Day Announces New Ice Cream Line Using Animal-Free Whey
summary: Perfect Day launches a new ice cream line featuring their precision-fermented, animal-free whey protein.

headline: Natural Fiber Welding Raises Series C Funding for Mirum Material Expansion
summary: Raises funds for expanding production of Mirum, a plant-based leather alternative free of plastic.

headline: Change Foods Secures Funding for Animal-Free Dairy Production
summary: Change Foods raised capital to scale precision fermentation for dairy alternatives like cheese and yogurt.

headline: Remilk Announces Expansion into New Global Markets
summary: Precision fermentation dairy company Remilk expands distribution to new regions, increasing availability.

headline: BioMason Secures Contract for Bio-Based Cement Production
summary: BioMason wins a major contract to produce bio-based cement alternatives using bacterial processes.
